data.description: NO HOA! BRAND NEW ROOF! Four-point and windmid  completed already and paid for    Beautiful Large Five Bedroom Three Bath Home were there is plenty of space for the whole family to get ready in the morning  the large backyard provides ample space for outdoor activities and is perfect for entertaining guests. Newly installed Shed in the backyard  on its on concrete SLAB.  The newly redone diamond bright pool adds a touch of luxury and is ideal for cooling off on hot summer days. Additionally, the home comes with All  brand new washer and dryer and appliances making laundry and cooking a breeze. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this beautiful home in a sought-after location. Contact us today to schedule a viewing.
